AGAINST THE D-REAPER SOMEHOW.

242
00:11:13,433 --> 00:11:14,835
MAYBE.

243
00:11:14,901 --> 00:11:17,237
I'D LIKE THIS TO STAY BETWEEN US
UNTIL WE'RE SURE.

244
00:11:17,237 --> 00:11:20,073
I DON'T WANT TO GIVE
THE OTHERS FALSE HOPE.

245
00:11:20,107 --> 00:11:22,576
OKAY. I'LL GET STARTED
ON IT RIGHT AWAY.

246
00:11:24,177 --> 00:11:26,213
