WITH EACH ATTACK.

263
00:12:01,415 --> 00:12:03,016
HENRY.

264
00:12:04,685 --> 00:12:06,253
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

265
00:12:06,253 --> 00:12:09,990
SUSIE, I CAN'T JUST SIT HERE
AND WATCH THIS ON TV ANYMORE.

266
00:12:10,023 --> 00:12:12,326
WE CAN'T IGNORE
THIS BATTLE.

267
00:12:12,359 --> 00:12:14,561
THOSE ARE OUR FRIENDS
AND OUR FAMILY

268
00:12:14,628 --> 00:12:16,463
THAT ARE FIGHTING
OUT THERE, SUSIE.

269
00:12:16,496 --> 00:12:17,964
THEY NEED HELP,

270
00:12:17,998 --> 00:12:20,734
AND YOU'RE THE ONLY ONE
WHO CAN GIVE ME STRENGTH.

271
00:12:20,801 --> 00:12:22,169
ME?

272
00:12:22,202 --> 00:12:25,305
YES. YOU'RE MY TAMER.
