273
00:12:25,339 --> 00:12:27,307
OKAY.

274
00:12:30,043 --> 00:12:31,478
DO I NEED A JACKET?

275
00:12:35,248 --> 00:12:37,150
NICE D-REAPER.

276
00:12:37,150 --> 00:12:38,185
OH, NO!

277
00:12:38,251 --> 00:12:40,454
HENRY!

278
00:12:40,487 --> 00:12:42,489
GUILMON!
HE'LL BE ERASED!

279
00:12:44,424 --> 00:12:48,528
