281
00:12:58,254 --> 00:13:00,322
Guilmon: NO ONE'S
ERASING MY BUDDIES!

282
00:13:03,539 --> 00:13:04,773
YOU OKAY?

283
00:13:04,773 --> 00:13:07,175
Terriermon: OH, YEAH,
