285
00:13:09,711 --> 00:13:11,680
MEGA BARRAGE!

286
00:13:13,682 --> 00:13:17,786
AAH!

287
00:13:24,059 --> 00:13:26,895
SHIELD OF THE JUST!

288
00:13:27,896 --> 00:13:29,765
AAH!

