00:13:50,085 --> 00:13:52,187
CAN THESE DIGIMON
TRULY DEFEAT THIS ENTITY

299
00:13:52,187 --> 00:13:55,791
OR ARE THEY JUST SIMPLY
DELAYING THE INEVITABLE?

300
00:13:55,791 --> 00:13:57,459
Gallantmon: SEE, D-REAPER?

301
00:13:57,492 --> 00:13:59,728
WE CAN TAKE
