SAKUYAMON.

318
00:14:42,003 --> 00:14:44,139
GET OUT OF HERE
BEFORE IT GRABS YOU, TOO!

319
00:14:44,172 --> 00:14:45,774
GALLANTMON, NO!

320
00:14:45,807 --> 00:14:49,644
THE D-REAPER IS
