321
00:14:50,979 --> 00:14:52,881
WE'VE GOT TO SAVE THEM

322
00:14:52,914 --> 00:14:54,916
BEFORE THEY'RE DELETED!

323
00:14:56,751 --> 00:14:59,287
HURRY UP ALREADY.
THE GUYS ARE IN TROUBLE.

