327
00:15:06,995 --> 00:15:08,129
SUSIE?

328
00:15:10,131 --> 00:15:12,133
SUSIE, ANSWER ME!

329
00:15:16,137 --> 00:15:19,107
OH, SUSIE.

330
00:15:19,140 --> 00:15:20,675
THANK GOODNESS.

331
00:15:20,742 --> 00:15:23,645
SUSIE, YOU OKAY?
