INSIDE THE D-REAPER OR THAT

344
00:15:59,881 --> 00:16:01,883
WE'RE INSIDE THE D-REAPER
AND WE'RE STILL ALIVE.

345
00:16:01,917 --> 00:16:03,985
Guilmon: TAKATO,
I DON'T KNOW

346
00:16:03,985 --> 00:16:06,421
IF I CAN HOLD
OUR MEGA FORM MUCH LONGER.

347
00:16:09,557 --> 00:16:11,693
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?
