348
00:16:11,693 --> 00:16:12,861
Guilmon: NO WAY.

349
00:16:12,894 --> 00:16:16,431
WELL, I DON'T THINK SO.
MAYBE. WE BETTER LAND.

350
00:16:19,034 --> 00:16:21,202
OKAY, BUT LAND
SOMEPLACE SAFE.

351
00:16:21,236 --> 00:16:22,537
HUH?

352
00:16:22,537 --> 00:16:24,039
HEY, WHAT ABOUT
OVER THERE?

353
00:16:24,039 --> 00:16:25,874
