COULDN'T BE ANALYZED.

362
00:16:43,091 --> 00:16:44,459
HUH?

363
00:16:44,492 --> 00:16:47,429
JERI! WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE?

364
00:16:47,462 --> 00:16:48,964
THIS IS THE MOST DANGEROUS
PLACE THERE IS.

365
00:16:48,997 --> 00:16:50,432
YOU SHOULDN'T BE HE--

