00:16:58,039 --> 00:16:59,941
COME ON, SHORTY,
PICK UP THE PACE, WOULD YOU?

368
00:16:59,975 --> 00:17:00,875
[ SIREN WAILING ]

369
00:17:00,909 --> 00:17:02,711
WHOA.

370
00:17:02,744 --> 00:17:04,346
HUH?

371
00:17:04,379 --> 00:17:07,048
HEY, WALKING MEANS NOT STOPPING
SUDDENLY, YOU KNOW?

372
00:17:07,048 --> 00:17:09,351
LOOK AT THAT, IMPMON.
I WANT TO GO OVER THERE.

373
00:17:09,384 --> 00:17:10,181
HUH?

374
00:17:10,181 --> 00:17:11,515
WHAT, ARE YOU CRAZY?

375
00:17:11,549 --> 00:17:13,951
THAT THING'S JUST
A GIANT ERASER TO US.

376
00:17:14,018 --> 00:17:15,753
Takato: WHY DID YOU
RUN AWAY BEFORE?

377
00:17:15,820 --> 00:17:17,254
DIDN'T YOU SEE ME?

378
00:17:17,321 --> 00:17:18,489
WELL, I GUESS
IT DOESN'T MATTER.

379
00:17:18,489 --> 00:17:19,824
I'M JUST GLAD
YOU'RE ALL RIGHT.

380
00:17:19,857 --> 00:17:21,192
