IT WAS EASY TO ASSIMILATE
THE BEING YOU CALL JERI

386
00:17:31,669 --> 00:17:34,305
BECAUSE HER DATA WAS SO SIMILAR
TO THE D-REAPER.

387
00:17:34,338 --> 00:17:36,640
HER THOUGHTS
WERE FOCUSED ON DESTRUCTION

388
00:17:36,674 --> 00:17:39,143
AND WHAT YOU HUMANS
