389
00:17:39,176 --> 00:17:40,678
JERI, WHAT'S THE MATTER
WITH YOU?

390
00:17:40,745 --> 00:17:42,680
SNAP OUT OF IT!
THIS ISN'T FUNNY!

391
00:17:42,747 --> 00:17:46,684
SHE HAS PROVEN
TO BE INVALUABLE

392
00:17:46,684 --> 00:17:50,654
IN THE D-REAPER'S
STUDY OF HUMANS.

393
00:17:50,721 --> 00:17:52,223
HEY, JERI, STOP!

394
00:17:52,223 --> 00:17:55,893
BUT YOUR KIND DOES REMAIN
DIFFICULT TO DECIPHER.

395
00:17:55,926 --> 00:17:58,195
TAKATO,
THAT'S NOT JERI.

396
00:17:58,229 --> 00:17:59,730
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT, GUILMON?

397
00:17:59,730 --> 00:18:01,966
