JUST LOOK AT HER.

398
00:18:01,999 --> 00:18:03,868
TAKATO, IT'S NOT!

399
00:18:03,901 --> 00:18:05,803
IT JUST HAS TO BE HER!

400
00:18:05,836 --> 00:18:07,471
Calumon: BUT I KNOW
I'M SUPPOSED TO BE THERE.

401
00:18:07,505 --> 00:18:08,873
YEAH, WELL,

402
00:18:08,939 --> 00:18:11,008
