WHAT THEY'RE SUPPOSED TO BE.

403
00:18:11,008 --> 00:18:14,345
YEAH, WELL, I DON'T CARE.
I'M GOING.

404
00:18:14,345 --> 00:18:15,746
HEY!

405
00:18:15,780 --> 00:18:17,681
YOU'RE BEING MEAN,
IMPMON!

406
00:18:17,748 --> 00:18:19,850
HEY, MEAN WOULD BE
LETTING YOU RUN IN THERE

407
00:18:19,850 --> 00:18:21,719
AND GET ERASED
QUICKER THAN YOU CAN SAY,

408
00:18:21,719 --> 00:18:25,389
"IS THIS A DELETE KEY
I SEE BEFORE ME?" SEE?

409
00:18:25,389 --> 00:18:27,725
WOW, IMPMON,
I DIDN'T KNOW YOU CARED.

410
00:18:27,725 --> 00:18:29,693
SURPRISED ME, TOO.

411
00:18:29,727 --> 00:18:31,228
I'LL BET.

412
00:18:32,897 --> 00:18:35,399
