THE BEING KNOWN AS JERI

413
00:18:35,399 --> 00:18:37,434
IN ORDER TO ANALYZE
THE LIFE FORMS

414
00:18:37,468 --> 00:18:40,538
THAT CREATED THE NETWORK
AND THE D-REAPER.

415
00:18:40,571 --> 00:18:43,374
