CONFUSING CREATURES --

416
00:18:43,407 --> 00:18:44,909
DISORDERLY, ILLOGICAL,

417
00:18:44,942 --> 00:18:47,545
AND WITHOUT RESPECT
FOR BOUNDARIES.

418
00:18:47,578 --> 00:18:50,080
