THAT WAY, JERI!

419
00:18:55,453 --> 00:18:59,290
[ Growls ] IT'S ONE
OF THE D-REAPER'S AGENTS!

420
00:19:04,628 --> 00:19:06,564
WHAT HAVE YOU DONE
WITH HER?

421
00:19:06,597 --> 00:19:09,266
BECAUSE
OF YOUR INHERENT DEFECTS,

422
00:19:09,300 --> 00:19:11,735
THE D-REAPER HAS DETERMINED
THAT ALL HUMANS

