RIGHT NOW OR YOU'LL BE SORRY.

426
00:19:20,244 --> 00:19:23,214
THE D-REAPER IS UNABLE
TO BE SORRY

427
00:19:23,247 --> 00:19:25,216
OR TO BE SAD OR HAPPY.

428
00:19:25,249 --> 00:19:27,051
