BUT MAKE YOU WEAK.

434
00:19:44,134 --> 00:19:46,103
WHAT YOU CALL WEAKNESSES

435
00:19:46,136 --> 00:19:48,105
ARE WHAT'S GOING TO HELP US
BEAT YOU.

436
00:19:48,138 --> 00:19:52,009
YOUR DEFIANCE IS POINTLESS.
YOU CANNOT WIN.

437
00:19:52,076 --> 00:19:53,377
THIS ISN'T OVER.

438
00:19:53,410 --> 00:19:55,312
IT'S GOING TO TAKE
MORE THAN WORDS TO STOP ME.

439
00:19:55,312 --> 00:19:56,380
HMM.

440
00:19:56,413 --> 00:19:58,983
TAKATO, WE GOT
TO GET OUT OF HERE NOW!

441
00:19:58,983 --> 00:20:01,952
I SWEAR I'LL SAVE JERI
IF IT'S THE LAST THING I DO!

442
00:20:02,019 --> 00:20:04,555
YOUR EMOTION
WILL GET YOU NOWHERE.

443
00:20:04,588 --> 00:20:07,191
