457
00:20:45,055 --> 00:20:45,902
Kazu: TYPICAL.

458
00:20:45,902 --> 00:20:47,371
ALWAYS SOMEONE
STEALING MY GLORY.

459
00:20:47,404 --> 00:20:49,439
IS THAT A FRIEND OR A FOE?

460
00:20:49,473 --> 00:20:51,908
